comments: Caldwell-Pope (LAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Simmons' (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Caruso (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball as he tips the rebound away from Embiid (PHI).
Harris (PHI) legally contests Schroder's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path.
Embiid (PHI) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Davis (LAL) arm makes contact with the ball during Embiid's (PHI) upward shooting motion.  Any contact after contacting the ball is incidental.
Embiid (PHI) turns and delivers contact to Caldwell-Pope (LAL) during the screen.
Caruso (LAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Simmons' (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Davis (LAL) firms up in Simmons' (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal defensive position alongside James (LAL) at the end of the drive.
Curry (PHI) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) slightly extends his off-arm as he steps back away from Davis (LAL) on the gather. The contact is marginal and Davis is able to defend the shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) makes marginal contact with Green's (PHI) arm as he secures and maintains possession of the rebound.
Harris (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Caruso's (LAL) path.
As Green (PHI) steps back and release from the contact, he makes marginal contact with Schroder (LAL) and Schroder is able to maintain his defensive position on-ball.
Schroder (LAL) legally contests Green's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) and Embiid (PHI) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Schroder (LAL) places his arm slightly away from his body as he establishes himself in a screening position in Embiid's (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Green (PHI) does not make contact with Davis (LAL) during his play at the basket.
Curry (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Davis' (LAL) path.
Caurso (LAL) extends an arm in Embiid's (PHI) path and makes marginal contact with Embiid during the inbound play. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Harris (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Caruso's (LAL) path and does not deliver any contact.
As Harris (PHI) receives the pass, he makes marginal contact to Caruso's (LAL) arm.
Caruso (LAL) maintains a legal defensive position alongside Harris (PHI) during his drive.
Caruso (LAL) legally contests Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal defensive position and does not deliver any contact as he defends Davis (LAL) on-ball.
Davis (LAL) begins to naturally lose his balance prior to the gather and Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal defensive position alongside Davis and does not deliver any contact during Davis' shot attempt.
